Distribution.
In North America, this species is mainly found in the low and subarctic of the West, with populations in southern Québec south to Virginia (
Fig. 33
). In the Palearctic Region, this species occurs in Fennoscandia, 
Russia
and 
Slovakia
(Šifner 2008; 
Engelmark & Haarto 2019
; 
Ozerov 2019
).
